193
00:14:30,495 --> 00:14:32,930
<b>It must have been hard
to turn down Mr. Lim's offer.</b>

194
00:14:32,965 --> 00:14:34,830
<b>A lot of thoughts crossed my mind
on my way there.</b>

195
00:14:35,065 --> 00:14:38,500
<b>But what I need is not Donghan.</b>

196
00:14:38,535 --> 00:14:40,400
<b>- It's Bella.
- Right.</b>

197
00:14:40,445 --> 00:14:42,840
<b>She needs to come see me this time.</b>

198
00:14:44,015 --> 00:14:45,610
<b>And about the contract, too.</b>

199
00:14:46,275 --> 00:14:49,585
